# Phase 2.7 — heartbeat trader runtime memory.
# These are runtime artifacts the live trader writes every shift.
# A bootstrap seed is committed at runtime/STATE.md.bootstrap.example;
# operator copies it to runtime/STATE.md on first deploy.
runtime/STATE.md
runtime/diary/*.md
!runtime/diary/.gitkeep
